name: Lightfoot Fever (1:34) digital video, 640 X 480, stereo @jimfetterley
description: Originally self released on VHS in 1996, this digital video went viral with tape traders & media festivals before being on compilation at vdb.org and othercinemadvd.com. Super-talented Jim Bailey dances with wild animals in Animal Charm's hot and exciting performance of "Fever."
